Package org.uclab.mm.icl.hlc.OntologyTools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Context
    Context is the class encapsulating the OntModel associated to a context instance.
    ContextOntology
    ContextOntology is the class encapsulating the OntModel associated to the Context Ontology which represents the Mining Minds Context Model.
    HighLevelContext
    High Level Context is the class encapsulating the OntModel associated to a High Level Context Instance.
    HLCA
    Vocabulary definitions for HLCA in Mining Minds v2.0.
    InferredContextOntology
    InferredContextOntology extends the ContextOntology class in order to provide the mechanisms to validate the Context Ontology which represents the Mining Minds Context Model.
    LowLevelContext
    Low Level Context is the class encapsulating the OntModel associated to a Low Level Context Instance.
    NutritionContext
    High Level Context is the class encapsulating the OntModel associated to a High Level Context Instance.
    PhysicalActivityContext
    High Level Context is the class encapsulating the OntModel associated to a High Level Context Instance.
